程序包 org.tron.trident.core.contract

类 Contract

java.lang.Object
org.tron.trident.core.contract.Contract
直接已知子类:
Trc20Contract
public class Contract extends Object
The Contract class is a wrapper for the SmartContract class defined in the .proto file. An object of Contract contains same attributes with the SmartContract class.

This class provides mutator and accessor methods for all attributes. Besides, functions of smart contracts are wrapped and can be easily viewed through ContractFunction.toString()</>

从以下版本开始:
jdk 1.8.0_231

    • deploy

      public TransactionBuilder deploy(List<org.tron.trident.abi.datatypes.Type> buildParams) throws Exception
      create a CreateSmartContract object to get ready for deployment. please note if any deposit is made during deployment(@see callValue), the constructor of this contract must be payable
      返回:
      TransactionBuilder object for signing and broadcasting
      抛出:
      Exception - if deployment duplicating / owner and origin address don't match
      ContractCreateException - if passes parameters but no constructor exists
